{
  "name": "GetSecrets",
  "description": "Get Secrets",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "page": {
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "Page of Secrets to retrieve (starts at and defaults to 0)"
      },
      "size": {
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "Size of a page. Maximum number of Secrets to include in a response (defaults to 20)"
      }
    }
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "http://microcks.local/secrets{?page,size}"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "List"
        },
        "A Secret allows grouping informations on how to access a restricted resource such as a repsoitory URL. Secrets are typically used by ImpoortJobs.",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**caCertPem**",
            "**description**: Description of this Secret",
            "**id**: Unique identifier of Secret",
            "**name**: Unique distinct name of Secret",
            "**password**",
            "**token**",
            "**tokenHeader**",
            "**username**"
          ]
        },
        {
          "$each": "$.body.*",
          "$as": "item",
          "$block": [
            {
              "$h2": {
                "$": "$.item.name"
              }
            },
            {
              "$lang": "json",
              "$code": {
                "$encode": "json",
                "$indent": true,
                "$content": {
                  "$": "$.item"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
